WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.650 --> 00:00:14.368
When it comes to Jesus' second coming and
the time of the apocalypse, I don't know

00:00:14.368 --> 00:00:18.227
how many theories there are on this topic.

00:00:18.227 --> 00:00:24.016
How many times have we heard
predictions about the end of the

00:00:24.016 --> 00:00:29.322
world, the apocalypse, and various
prophets about whom Jesus warns us,

00:00:29.322 --> 00:00:33.181
but He warns us not to believe anyone.

00:00:33.181 --> 00:00:33.663
Why?

00:00:33.663 --> 00:00:39.935
Because today Jesus speaks and compares
the day of His coming to lightning.

00:00:41.075 --> 00:00:44.400
Why does he compare it to lightning?

00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:48.676
Because in Palestine at that
time, the climatic conditions

00:00:48.676 --> 00:00:51.527
were such that it rarely rained.

00:00:51.527 --> 00:00:56.753
But when there was a sign of
rain, lightning would suddenly

00:00:56.753 --> 00:01:01.504
strike, it would get dark,
and... Everyone would get scared.

00:01:01.504 --> 00:01:07.205
And precisely, Jesus compares his
coming today in the gospel to lightning.

00:01:07.205 --> 00:01:14.332
That it will be sudden, that everyone
will see and experience it, and not as

00:01:14.332 --> 00:01:20.984
some false prophets today interpret it,
saying it will be this year, it will

00:01:20.984 --> 00:01:24.785
be like this, it will be like that.

00:01:25.085 --> 00:01:30.968
So, the first thing we as Christians
need to believe is the Gospel.

00:01:30.968 --> 00:01:37.304
And that is, Jesus says he will
definitely come, but when, no one knows.

00:01:37.304 --> 00:01:40.019
And thirdly, it will be sudden.

00:01:40.019 --> 00:01:43.187
So, what is Jesus talking about here?

00:01:43.187 --> 00:01:46.808
He is talking about the Kingdom of Heaven.

00:01:46.808 --> 00:01:50.428
That it was already
established with his coming.

00:01:50.428 --> 00:01:55.859
All those who lived at that
time didn't even notice that the

00:01:55.859 --> 00:01:58.575
Kingdom of God had already arrived.

00:01:59.465 --> 00:02:05.554
Even today, many people, even some in the
church, do not notice that the Kingdom

00:02:05.554 --> 00:02:08.802
of God is here, that Jesus is alive.

00:02:08.802 --> 00:02:13.268
Today, there are plenty of people,
from believers to non-believers, who

00:02:13.268 --> 00:02:16.109
doubt whether Jesus is alive at all.

00:02:16.109 --> 00:02:19.357
So, when will He come a second time?

00:02:19.357 --> 00:02:26.259
If we do not live with the awareness that
Jesus is coming and what He is talking

00:02:26.259 --> 00:02:28.695
about regarding the Kingdom of God?

00:02:28.775 --> 00:02:34.312
Because we, who are Gentiles,
sometimes behave just as the Jews did.

00:02:34.312 --> 00:02:36.158
What do we expect?

00:02:36.158 --> 00:02:40.773
Some kind of world revolution,
a kingdom of peace, established

00:02:40.773 --> 00:02:42.157
security and prosperity.

00:02:42.157 --> 00:02:48.156
Let's remember that at that moment the
Jews were under occupation, they were

00:02:48.156 --> 00:02:53.694
constantly under occupation, and at
that time they were under the Romans.

00:02:53.694 --> 00:03:00.154
They expected Christ to come as a military
leader to establish that kingdom, and

00:03:00.154 --> 00:03:03.385
that it would be an external kingdom.

00:03:04.565 --> 00:03:08.504
The organisation of the state,
the organisation of the kingdom.

00:03:08.504 --> 00:03:12.837
That it would be a revolution
when the promised Messiah comes.

00:03:12.837 --> 00:03:16.776
Even today, many ask,
where is God in this world?

00:03:16.776 --> 00:03:20.322
Why doesn't He intervene
a bit, calm these wars?

00:03:20.322 --> 00:03:23.079
Why doesn't He organise society a bit?

00:03:23.079 --> 00:03:25.443
Why doesn't He make people convert?

00:03:25.443 --> 00:03:25.837
No.

00:03:25.837 --> 00:03:28.595
Jesus brought a different
kind of revolution.

00:03:30.155 --> 00:03:31.551
Revolutions of the heart.

00:03:31.551 --> 00:03:34.344
That is what many are
confused about today.

00:03:34.344 --> 00:03:37.137
They are confused by
sin, because sin blinds.

00:03:37.137 --> 00:03:41.675
Even today, many do not see
that the Kingdom of God has been

00:03:41.675 --> 00:03:43.421
established, that Jesus is alive.

00:03:43.421 --> 00:03:45.166
Why do they not see?

00:03:45.166 --> 00:03:47.959
Because they do not
believe with their hearts.

00:03:47.959 --> 00:03:52.149
As the scripture beautifully says,
"This people honour me with their lips,

00:03:52.149 --> 00:03:57.036
but their hearts are far from me." And
Jesus is precisely speaking about the

00:03:57.036 --> 00:04:01.575
revolution of the Kingdom of God that
is established in the human heart.

00:04:02.055 --> 00:04:06.243
And that revolution of the
Kingdom of God is love.

00:04:06.243 --> 00:04:12.106
Many do not open themselves to love
today, they do not open themselves to

00:04:12.106 --> 00:04:17.550
God, and therefore they cannot notice
that the Kingdom of God is alive.

00:04:17.550 --> 00:04:24.251
That among us are so many saints, so many
people who have opened themselves to God's

00:04:24.251 --> 00:04:29.695
grace, God's love, they have established
the Kingdom of God in their hearts.

00:04:29.695 --> 00:04:35.140
Jesus does not want to guarantee us
material goods like the European Union,

00:04:35.140 --> 00:04:42.260
but wants to give us the kingdom of love,
which this world is taking away from us.

00:04:42.260 --> 00:04:47.450
Because today we are spiritually
orphaned, we are spiritually hungry

00:04:47.450 --> 00:04:50.565
and thirsty for God and love.

00:04:50.565 --> 00:04:56.274
Jesus tells us that prosperity,
security, and armament will not bring

00:04:56.274 --> 00:04:59.908
peace to our hearts, but He will.

00:04:59.908 --> 00:05:03.022
How many open themselves to Him?

00:05:03.022 --> 00:05:07.175
How many today see the Kingdom of God?

00:05:07.175 --> 00:05:13.922
Do you feel the Kingdom of God
in your heart at this moment?

00:05:13.922 --> 00:05:20.670
Jesus warns us in today's Gospel
to be patient, as many have become

00:05:20.670 --> 00:05:23.785
impatient waiting for His second coming.

00:05:24.385 --> 00:05:29.997
Is it really so important to us how
we, as believers, sometimes start to

00:05:29.997 --> 00:05:34.407
concern ourselves with trivial questions
that aren't crucial for our salvation?

00:05:34.407 --> 00:05:39.218
Did Jesus get dirty in the
mud when he was a child?

00:05:39.218 --> 00:05:41.624
Knowing that will surely save you.

00:05:41.624 --> 00:05:46.435
You'll definitely convert if you
know the date when Jesus will come.

00:05:46.435 --> 00:05:47.236
You won't.

00:05:47.236 --> 00:05:52.849
Those who are just curious like Baba
Vanga and others, they just babble with

00:05:52.849 --> 00:05:55.255
their mouths, not with their hearts.

00:05:55.755 --> 00:06:01.938
Because if you knew He was coming
tomorrow, would you have time to repent,

00:06:01.938 --> 00:06:05.471
to open your heart, to cast away sin?

00:06:05.471 --> 00:06:08.121
And what does Jesus teach us?

00:06:08.121 --> 00:06:15.188
Jesus wants us to learn one thing for
when He comes, to be where we are,

00:06:15.188 --> 00:06:18.280
in our position, to be ready then.

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:24.463
Not to abandon our jobs, not to leave all
our responsibilities, because Jesus is

00:06:24.463 --> 00:06:27.555
coming tomorrow, the end of the world.

00:06:27.555 --> 00:06:30.072
And what does He mean by that?

00:06:30.072 --> 00:06:32.950
That we should be ready at any moment.

00:06:32.950 --> 00:06:35.108
It doesn't matter what tomorrow brings.

00:06:35.108 --> 00:06:39.425
Whether it will be in 5
years or 10, it will happen.

00:06:39.425 --> 00:06:45.180
But what matters to Jesus is that He
warns us today: when He comes, will the

00:06:45.180 --> 00:06:48.058
Son of Man find faith on this earth?

00:06:48.058 --> 00:06:53.094
Will He find those who have opened
their hearts to the Kingdom of God?

00:06:53.094 --> 00:06:58.130
That's what's important to you and me,
that we are ready whenever it happens.

00:06:58.975 --> 00:07:03.217
Will you die tomorrow or
will Jesus come tonight?

00:07:03.217 --> 00:07:04.632
It doesn't matter.

00:07:04.632 --> 00:07:07.932
Just be ready and in your position.

00:07:07.932 --> 00:07:13.589
That's why I say, many have been
impatient at times, as history

00:07:13.589 --> 00:07:15.475
has shown in Christianity.

00:07:15.475 --> 00:07:20.660
We shouldn't lose patience, but
rather open ourselves to that kingdom.

00:07:20.660 --> 00:07:26.317
If you start living it here
on earth now, nothing grand or

00:07:26.317 --> 00:07:28.675
spectacular will change up there.

00:07:28.715 --> 00:07:32.124
It will only continue with
stronger, better intensity.

00:07:32.124 --> 00:07:34.255
Beware of those who deceive.

00:07:34.255 --> 00:07:37.238
Beware of those who prophesy to you.

00:07:37.238 --> 00:07:42.352
Those who interpret for you, who
choose the number of the saved.

00:07:42.352 --> 00:07:47.039
We have so many theses about
this, so many false teachings.

00:07:47.039 --> 00:07:49.170
Jesus warned us about this.

00:07:49.170 --> 00:07:52.153
And today, people blindly run after it.

00:07:52.153 --> 00:07:58.120
You see, she has the gift of prophecy,
she said this, she said that...

00:07:58.120 --> 00:08:01.005
People, have a little faith in the Gospel.

00:08:01.005 --> 00:08:04.251
You believe every old woman,
every prophetess, every guru.

00:08:04.251 --> 00:08:09.301
But the Word of God is imprinted
in your heart, as St. Paul says.

00:08:09.301 --> 00:08:10.743
Stay faithful to that.

00:08:10.743 --> 00:08:15.793
Many will end up in hell because
they are not faithful to God's Word.

00:08:15.793 --> 00:08:19.400
They seek alternatives, they
want to speed up the path.

00:08:22.310 --> 00:08:25.469
The Lord therefore
wants to test our faith.

00:08:26.810 --> 00:08:33.422
He says that when the second coming
happens, no one will foresee it, but

00:08:33.422 --> 00:08:36.728
everyone will see it when it occurs.

00:08:36.728 --> 00:08:41.924
So, many today think they can
benefit from a good connection.

00:08:41.924 --> 00:08:49.008
That if you are in communion with someone,
you will be saved because of them.

00:08:49.008 --> 00:08:55.621
Many think if I am in some association
or community, I will be saved.

00:08:55.621 --> 00:08:58.455
Don't forget, salvation
is individual, personal.

00:08:58.495 --> 00:09:04.489
Remember when the Gospel says in another
place, it warns that when the Lord comes,

00:09:04.489 --> 00:09:10.085
he will separate the husband from the
wife, the child from the father and

00:09:10.085 --> 00:09:14.881
mother, he will separate... This means
you won't benefit from anyone else.

00:09:14.881 --> 00:09:18.877
You won't benefit from any
association or anything like that.

00:09:18.877 --> 00:09:23.673
It means you will personally see
the Lord and experience him, but

00:09:23.673 --> 00:09:28.070
you will also personally give
an account to that same Lord.

00:09:29.570 --> 00:09:33.760
It's important that we are ready
in the morning, at noon, in

00:09:33.760 --> 00:09:35.505
the evening, at every moment.

00:09:35.505 --> 00:09:36.902
That should concern us.

00:09:36.902 --> 00:09:39.695
Not the time and date of His coming.

00:09:39.695 --> 00:09:43.187
But are we ready now for the Lord to come?

00:09:43.187 --> 00:09:47.028
He will come in the Eucharist,
He will come in adoration.

00:09:47.028 --> 00:09:49.821
Are we ready to open ourselves to Him?

00:09:49.821 --> 00:09:54.710
Many times I see, even here at these
DDBs and in general, people come.

00:09:54.710 --> 00:09:55.944
Not everyone opens up.

00:09:55.944 --> 00:09:57.486
Not everyone opens their heart.

00:09:57.486 --> 00:10:02.114
There are those who open up and cry and
experience grace because God is alive.

00:10:02.114 --> 00:10:04.273
God wants to saturate us with love.

00:10:04.273 --> 00:10:08.592
But there are also those icebergs who
come out of curiosity, who come and

00:10:08.592 --> 00:10:10.752
don't know what to do with themselves.

00:10:10.752 --> 00:10:15.071
So they think, "Let's go there, it's
crowded, I'll go and push my way

00:10:15.071 --> 00:10:17.230
in." It doesn't matter where it is.

00:10:17.230 --> 00:10:19.390
But man, you're missing out on grace.

00:10:21.370 --> 00:10:26.718
So, the Kingdom of God is being
offered to you, and yet you are

00:10:26.718 --> 00:10:30.156
afraid to open up to God, who is love.

00:10:30.156 --> 00:10:31.302
Why is that?

00:10:31.302 --> 00:10:31.684
Why?

00:10:31.684 --> 00:10:35.122
It's so simple, yet we
make it so complicated.

00:10:35.122 --> 00:10:37.033
That's why I'm telling you.

00:10:37.033 --> 00:10:40.089
Wherever you go, what are you looking for?

00:10:40.089 --> 00:10:43.527
The Kingdom of God is not
some external spectacle.

00:10:43.527 --> 00:10:45.055
It's an inner reality.

00:10:45.055 --> 00:10:49.257
There are also those who go
from one spiritual renewal to

00:10:49.257 --> 00:10:51.550
another just to see a spectacle.

00:10:53.370 --> 00:10:57.373
So, the relationship with the
Lord and the Kingdom of God

00:10:57.373 --> 00:10:59.192
is not an external spectacle.

00:10:59.192 --> 00:11:01.012
That's what the Jews expected.

00:11:01.012 --> 00:11:05.379
Give us some spectacle of
the kingdom, so we can see it

00:11:05.379 --> 00:11:07.927
visually, what it is, how it is.

00:11:07.927 --> 00:11:12.658
No, the Lord speaks precisely about
the interior of our heart, our soul.

00:11:12.658 --> 00:11:13.022
Why?

00:11:13.022 --> 00:11:16.661
Because God does not conquer
by force but by love.

00:11:16.661 --> 00:11:20.665
His kingdom does not come from
the outside, but from within.

00:11:20.945 --> 00:11:23.285
That's why it confuses many people.

00:11:23.285 --> 00:11:26.796
That's why many people can't
see this kingdom present.

00:11:26.796 --> 00:11:27.966
But it lives.

00:11:27.966 --> 00:11:34.207
It lives in you, it lives in him,
it lives in her, it lives in them.

00:11:34.207 --> 00:11:35.767
It is already present.

00:11:35.767 --> 00:11:41.618
And that's why many have difficulty seeing
it because it is not some grand spectacle.

00:11:41.618 --> 00:11:44.739
Rather, it is a personal
relationship with God.

00:11:44.739 --> 00:11:50.199
That's why it is said that the
Kingdom of God begins in our hearts.

00:11:50.520 --> 00:11:54.549
The Kingdom of God means that God reigns.

00:11:54.549 --> 00:11:55.053
When?

00:11:55.053 --> 00:11:58.579
When does God reign in my heart?

00:11:58.579 --> 00:12:00.594
Let's examine our conscience.

00:12:00.594 --> 00:12:03.113
What reigns in my heart?

00:12:03.113 --> 00:12:05.128
God or my ego?

00:12:05.128 --> 00:12:06.135
My fear?

00:12:06.135 --> 00:12:07.143
My pride?

00:12:07.143 --> 00:12:08.150
My selfishness?

00:12:08.150 --> 00:12:09.158
My security?

00:12:09.158 --> 00:12:14.699
What reigns at this moment
in my heart and in yours?

00:12:14.699 --> 00:12:21.751
Is it the Kingdom of God, trust
in God, or all the other spirits

00:12:21.751 --> 00:12:24.270
and things that destroy us?

00:12:24.880 --> 00:12:28.248
Have we opened ourselves
to God who is love?

00:12:28.248 --> 00:12:31.242
Did your heart burn as you came here?

00:12:31.242 --> 00:12:35.733
Does it burn while you are
here for three hours in prayer?

00:12:35.733 --> 00:12:40.224
If it doesn't burn, mate, then
the devil is burning within you.

00:12:40.224 --> 00:12:42.096
Some other spirit is burning.

00:12:42.096 --> 00:12:46.587
Because it's impossible, I don't
understand how someone can be in prayer

00:12:46.587 --> 00:12:48.833
for three hours and feel nothing.

00:12:48.833 --> 00:12:49.207
How?

00:12:49.207 --> 00:12:52.950
It only means that you have
deliberately locked your heart.

00:12:52.950 --> 00:12:57.946
Saint Peter will lock the
gates of heaven for you too.

00:12:57.946 --> 00:12:59.308
You're punishing yourself.

00:12:59.308 --> 00:13:00.217
Until when?

00:13:00.217 --> 00:13:02.033
It's such a problem.

00:13:02.033 --> 00:13:03.396
Belong to Jesus.

00:13:03.396 --> 00:13:07.938
Choose his kingdom, the
kingdom of love in your heart.

00:13:07.938 --> 00:13:12.934
Whenever you choose God, choose
love, when you stop being afraid,

00:13:12.934 --> 00:13:18.838
you will be blessed, the kingdom
of God will grow in your heart.

00:13:18.838 --> 00:13:23.834
When you stop sinning, when
you do good, the kingdom of

00:13:23.834 --> 00:13:26.560
God will grow in your heart.

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:30.493
When you stop hating and
choose to forgive, the Kingdom

00:13:30.493 --> 00:13:32.460
of God grows within you.

00:13:32.460 --> 00:13:34.820
And so on and so forth.

00:13:34.820 --> 00:13:39.934
Are we striving for the Kingdom
of God to grow in our hearts?

00:13:39.934 --> 00:13:41.114
It is possible.

00:13:41.114 --> 00:13:47.408
We all need to improve and change
day by day, to belong to God, for the

00:13:47.408 --> 00:13:50.555
Kingdom of God to come alive within us.

00:13:50.555 --> 00:13:56.063
We are constantly in a state of limbo,
always waiting to die, for something

00:13:56.063 --> 00:13:59.209
with God to come alive when we die.

00:13:59.209 --> 00:14:01.798
Nothing will come to life then.

00:14:01.798 --> 00:14:05.680
Now we pray to the Lord to change us.

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:11.287
If you noticed a sentence in the
Gospel where it says that Jesus

00:14:11.287 --> 00:14:17.326
says, but first the Son of Man must
suffer greatly, be rejected by this

00:14:17.326 --> 00:14:19.915
generation, and then he will come.

00:14:19.915 --> 00:14:25.522
You see, we might be living
in a time where it is evident

00:14:25.522 --> 00:14:27.679
how many people reject Jesus.

00:14:27.679 --> 00:14:29.404
How many reject faith.

00:14:29.404 --> 00:14:34.581
How many consider themselves enlightened
and those who believe, of course, they

00:14:34.581 --> 00:14:40.620
consider stupid and naive, and then they
say, you're still in the Middle Ages.

00:14:40.680 --> 00:14:45.356
Thank God that we have faith and
that we are considered foolish.

00:14:45.356 --> 00:14:50.812
I'm really glad that I'm not enlightened
by the same spirit they live by.

00:14:50.812 --> 00:14:52.371
The spirit of death.

00:14:52.371 --> 00:14:55.879
I wouldn't have the courage
to declare Jesus dead.

00:14:55.879 --> 00:15:00.945
That's why I'm telling you, Jesus
says, there will come a time when

00:15:00.945 --> 00:15:05.622
they will first reject me, and
then the false ones will appear

00:15:05.622 --> 00:15:08.740
and say, here he is, there he is.

00:15:09.200 --> 00:15:11.125
Do not follow such people.

00:15:11.125 --> 00:15:11.510
Why?

00:15:11.510 --> 00:15:15.745
Because Jesus says that the kingdom
comes through rejection, that the

00:15:15.745 --> 00:15:20.365
kingdom of God comes through the
cross, and that is our comfort.

00:15:20.365 --> 00:15:25.370
For if someone hates you because you
believe, if someone persecutes you because

00:15:25.370 --> 00:15:30.760
you believe, if someone is jealous of
you just because you believe, if someone

00:15:30.760 --> 00:15:36.150
mocks you just because they saw you in
church, if someone mocks you because

00:15:36.150 --> 00:15:41.925
you made the sign of the cross in the
canteen, great, remember what Jesus says.

00:15:42.385 --> 00:15:44.342
They should reject me first.

00:15:44.342 --> 00:15:48.647
So why wouldn't they reject
me and you because of Jesus?

00:15:48.647 --> 00:15:51.387
It means that God lives in you.

00:15:51.387 --> 00:15:55.301
As soon as this world rejects
you, society, friends, relatives,

00:15:55.301 --> 00:15:59.607
brother, sister, parents, well, thank
God, let them reject us forever.

00:15:59.607 --> 00:16:01.173
We belong to Jesus.

00:16:01.173 --> 00:16:05.478
And if they will reject
Jesus, let them reject us too.

00:16:05.478 --> 00:16:08.610
It can only be a plus for us.

00:16:10.270 --> 00:16:14.127
Because while this world embraces
us, while sinful society pulls us

00:16:14.127 --> 00:16:15.880
towards itself, that's the problem.

00:16:15.880 --> 00:16:18.685
Then we are in the clutches of evil.

00:16:18.685 --> 00:16:23.243
When that same world cannot tolerate
us just because we belong to Jesus.

00:16:23.243 --> 00:16:27.802
They want to spit us out from their
mouths, from society, from everything.

00:16:27.802 --> 00:16:29.555
Eliminate everything that is Christian.

00:16:29.555 --> 00:16:29.905
Great!

00:16:29.905 --> 00:16:30.256
Fantastic!

00:16:30.256 --> 00:16:32.360
We are on the right path.

00:16:32.360 --> 00:16:37.620
I don't know how to make those
who are in the jaws of evil aware.

00:16:37.820 --> 00:16:40.193
Those who follow the broad path.

00:16:40.193 --> 00:16:42.172
Because evil always embraces you.

00:16:42.172 --> 00:16:46.920
Evil people always seek you out,
evil people and the devil always

00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:52.459
reward you, and many do not see this,
unfortunately, they do not see it.

00:16:52.459 --> 00:16:57.207
That is why the Kingdom of God goes
through suffering, through rejection,

00:16:57.207 --> 00:17:02.350
through sacrifice, and that is a comfort
to every Christian who has sincerely

00:17:02.350 --> 00:17:05.120
opened themselves to the Kingdom of God.

00:17:05.120 --> 00:17:07.890
Suffering, rejection, everything
that Jesus went through.

00:17:08.630 --> 00:17:12.351
You walk the path of Jesus
and it cannot be otherwise.

00:17:12.351 --> 00:17:14.043
But do not be afraid.

00:17:14.043 --> 00:17:16.750
Do not be afraid when the Lord comes.

00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:18.442
You will not tremble then.

00:17:18.442 --> 00:17:20.133
You will be at peace.

00:17:20.133 --> 00:17:23.855
Or when you are dying, you
will die in peace because

00:17:23.855 --> 00:17:25.885
you know where you are going.

00:17:25.885 --> 00:17:30.961
The Kingdom of God is not seen by
who has power, but by who knows

00:17:30.961 --> 00:17:32.991
how to love even when rejected.

00:17:32.991 --> 00:17:38.405
Sometimes it seems to us today that
we are so small in the face of evil.

00:17:38.655 --> 00:17:43.321
So small in this world of power,
money, politics, everything.

00:17:43.321 --> 00:17:45.655
However, power isn't in that.

00:17:45.655 --> 00:17:48.922
Power is to love and be rejected.

00:17:48.922 --> 00:17:51.722
Power is to love and forgive.

00:17:51.722 --> 00:17:54.522
That is the Kingdom of God.

00:17:54.522 --> 00:17:57.322
That breaks the axes of evil.

00:17:57.322 --> 00:18:02.922
That breaks the haters of
Jesus, the haters of you and me.

00:18:02.922 --> 00:18:03.389
Love.

00:18:03.389 --> 00:18:06.189
Just imagine how strong that is.

00:18:06.189 --> 00:18:08.056
How strong that is.

00:18:08.056 --> 00:18:10.389
To love and be rejected.

00:18:10.389 --> 00:18:13.187
And this world teaches everything
completely differently.

00:18:13.187 --> 00:18:17.583
To seek revenge, to hate, to
push for yourself, to fight.

00:18:17.583 --> 00:18:23.577
But you see, the source of all that
is what you live in your heart.

00:18:23.577 --> 00:18:28.772
When you open yourself to God, that
personal relationship with God, it becomes

00:18:28.772 --> 00:18:35.166
clear to you what the Lord wants from
you only when you are alone with Him.

00:18:35.166 --> 00:18:37.564
Not what others have told you.

00:18:37.564 --> 00:18:41.960
Let's be clear, we will not
all bear the same cross.

00:18:43.150 --> 00:18:46.088
Not everyone bears the same cross equally.

00:18:46.088 --> 00:18:51.965
Nor do we all have the same intensity
of God's grace in our hearts.

00:18:51.965 --> 00:18:57.842
But the Lord will accomplish through
each of us what He needs and desires.

00:18:57.842 --> 00:19:02.040
It's very interesting, if you've
listened, that it says there,

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:08.538
The Kingdom of God is not
within one person, but the

00:19:08.538 --> 00:19:10.468
Kingdom of God is among you.

00:19:10.468 --> 00:19:12.720
You've heard that sentence in the Gospel.

00:19:12.920 --> 00:19:16.272
He says, the Kingdom of
God is among you, plural.

00:19:16.272 --> 00:19:19.624
There are people who have
opened the Kingdom of God.

00:19:19.624 --> 00:19:21.636
And those people are the church.

00:19:21.636 --> 00:19:27.000
Because Jesus says, where two or three
are gathered in my name, I am with them.

00:19:30.275 --> 00:19:32.290
And today Jesus speaks about rejection.

00:19:32.290 --> 00:19:33.970
How many people reject fellowship?

00:19:33.970 --> 00:19:38.001
The Church is a fellowship of
believers, the mystical body of Christ.

00:19:38.001 --> 00:19:41.696
We're not talking about a building,
we're talking about spiritual fellowship.

00:19:41.696 --> 00:19:46.064
You young people know how to
say, wow, how much easier it is

00:19:46.064 --> 00:19:48.079
to talk to someone who believes.

00:19:48.079 --> 00:19:49.423
You understand each other.

00:19:49.423 --> 00:19:53.790
You strive to find a boyfriend or
girlfriend for marriage and in faith

00:19:53.790 --> 00:19:57.821
because you will understand each other
more easily, both spiritually and in

00:19:57.821 --> 00:20:00.845
terms of the values you want to live by.

00:20:00.845 --> 00:20:02.525
And that is completely normal.

00:20:02.845 --> 00:20:07.606
That's why it says here in the
plural, in the plural it says that

00:20:07.606 --> 00:20:09.987
the Kingdom of God is among you.

00:20:09.987 --> 00:20:15.089
That is the church, that is the mystical
body of Christ which should be respected.

00:20:15.089 --> 00:20:19.510
And how many today are leaving that
church, how many are attacking it.

00:20:19.510 --> 00:20:24.612
I don't know if the people who are
attacking it are often aware or not

00:20:24.612 --> 00:20:26.652
that they are instruments of Satan.

00:20:26.652 --> 00:20:31.074
Because when you attack the church,
you are not attacking the priest, the

00:20:31.074 --> 00:20:33.455
bishop, or this person or that person.

00:20:33.695 --> 00:20:36.779
You are attacking the
mystical body of Christ.

00:20:36.779 --> 00:20:39.864
For the Kingdom of God is within you.

00:20:39.864 --> 00:20:43.719
The Holy Spirit is within
you, within you, within you.

00:20:43.719 --> 00:20:45.261
Love is within you.

00:20:45.261 --> 00:20:49.117
And imagine how much that word,
love, is prostituted today.

00:20:49.117 --> 00:20:52.587
I only acknowledge it
in the context of God.

00:20:52.587 --> 00:20:57.600
It is the only true love that gives
itself completely on the cross.

00:20:57.600 --> 00:21:03.716
All these other mantras in the name
of love, in the name of rights, in

00:21:03.716 --> 00:21:09.425
the name of this, in the name of
that, the word is often misused.

00:21:09.425 --> 00:21:13.503
True love serves, loves, does
not attack, does not hate.

00:21:13.503 --> 00:21:17.173
I don't understand, imagine,
God by definition is love

00:21:17.173 --> 00:21:19.620
and yet has so many enemies.

00:21:22.810 --> 00:21:24.176
Who cannot bear love?

00:21:24.176 --> 00:21:24.518
Evil.

00:21:24.518 --> 00:21:24.860
Evil.

00:21:24.860 --> 00:21:25.885
Do you understand?

00:21:25.885 --> 00:21:31.011
Is it so hard to understand when
you look at the cross, even if you

00:21:31.011 --> 00:21:35.795
never read the Bible, you look at
the cross and see that this man

00:21:35.795 --> 00:21:37.504
only loved, gave himself completely.

00:21:37.504 --> 00:21:39.213
And yet someone hates him.

00:21:39.213 --> 00:21:43.314
And yet someone cannot stand to
see him in school corridors, cannot

00:21:43.314 --> 00:21:47.415
stand to see him in institutions,
cannot stand to see him anywhere.

00:21:47.435 --> 00:21:47.946
Why?

00:21:47.946 --> 00:21:53.570
Because evil is glaring from
your eyes as you serve Satan.

00:21:53.570 --> 00:21:54.593
It's strange.

00:21:54.593 --> 00:21:59.706
1 John 4:16 speaks of love,
yet someone constantly feels

00:21:59.706 --> 00:22:02.774
the need to remove this image.

00:22:02.774 --> 00:22:04.820
To remove the crucifix.

00:22:04.820 --> 00:22:05.331
Why?

00:22:05.331 --> 00:22:07.888
Because Jesus broke their power.

00:22:07.888 --> 00:22:15.558
And even when they seem strong in
this world for a moment, they are not.

00:22:15.558 --> 00:22:20.160
Because God is coming, Jesus
announces His glorious return.

00:22:20.300 --> 00:22:24.749
It will come eventually,
everyone will bow down.

00:22:24.749 --> 00:22:28.085
Jesus' arrival will be like lightning.

00:22:28.085 --> 00:22:30.866
Suddenly, everyone will be frightened.

00:22:30.866 --> 00:22:38.652
Those who are His, who live in love,
will recognise Him and wait bravely.

00:22:38.652 --> 00:22:44.769
Only those who have persecuted
Him all these years will wail.

00:22:44.769 --> 00:22:48.662
So, thank God for Jesus' second coming.

00:22:48.662 --> 00:22:54.780
The Kingdom of God is interesting
because it conquers with love.

00:22:56.000 --> 00:23:00.442
Jesus did not come into
this world with an army.

00:23:00.442 --> 00:23:07.105
Jesus did not defeat evil with an
army but with love, a love that does

00:23:07.105 --> 00:23:10.658
not give up even when it is rejected.

00:23:10.658 --> 00:23:14.212
How many times has God's
love been rejected?

00:23:14.212 --> 00:23:19.986
How many times has it remained outside
the closed doors of our hearts?

00:23:19.986 --> 00:23:24.428
However, let us remember when
Jesus came the first time.

00:23:24.428 --> 00:23:26.650
He came to be judged.

00:23:27.570 --> 00:23:33.088
And the second time Jesus
comes, He will come to judge us.

00:23:33.088 --> 00:23:34.927
Do not forget that.

00:23:34.927 --> 00:23:42.285
The first time we judged Him, but the
second time He comes, He will judge us.

00:23:42.285 --> 00:23:46.424
And that will be the end of the story.

00:23:46.424 --> 00:23:53.322
However, I would like to warn you about
one more thing I mentioned here, that

00:23:53.322 --> 00:23:56.541
the Kingdom of God is in fellowship.

00:23:56.541 --> 00:24:02.979
For those of us within the church,
there is one thing I must highlight

00:24:02.979 --> 00:24:05.738
which is an absolutely great danger.

00:24:05.738 --> 00:24:11.716
We often use the phrase, "I know
the faith, I know the Bible,"

00:24:11.716 --> 00:24:16.315
and sometimes that knowledge
actually keeps us distant from God.

00:24:17.255 --> 00:24:20.575
Are the Nazarenes where Jesus comes from?

00:24:20.575 --> 00:24:23.421
Everyone knew Jesus, everyone knew him.

00:24:23.421 --> 00:24:29.113
He couldn't do anything there
because they said, oh, we know you,

00:24:29.113 --> 00:24:34.805
you're from this place, from that
place, and he couldn't do anything.

00:24:34.805 --> 00:24:36.702
But they knew him.

00:24:36.702 --> 00:24:39.074
They didn't change at all.

00:24:39.074 --> 00:24:41.920
In the end, who betrayed Jesus?

00:24:41.920 --> 00:24:43.817
Who handed Jesus over?

00:24:43.817 --> 00:24:45.715
Those who knew him.

00:24:47.075 --> 00:24:53.136
I'm afraid that many in the church
will also think they know Jesus

00:24:53.136 --> 00:24:56.400
and use the phrase, "I know him."

00:24:58.960 --> 00:25:03.020
I've experienced more than once asking
someone to talk about faith, and they

00:25:03.020 --> 00:25:07.394
say, "Well, Father, well, Brother, well,
no, I know that, I've gone through the

00:25:07.394 --> 00:25:12.080
Bible, do you still read it?" "Well,
no, once is enough, I know it now."

00:25:12.900 --> 00:25:19.435
And then you try to encourage them by
saying, "Well, I read every day and study

00:25:19.435 --> 00:25:25.971
the faith." And they say, "Poor you,
you went to school for so many years and

00:25:25.971 --> 00:25:31.690
still don't know Jesus." People think they
know God if they've read something once.

00:25:31.690 --> 00:25:35.774
But we must strive our whole
lives, absorb, contemplate, pray,

00:25:35.774 --> 00:25:41.085
live sacramentally to truly know
Jesus, and we say we know Him best.

00:25:41.725 --> 00:25:45.739
You might be familiar,
but you don't truly know.

00:25:45.739 --> 00:25:51.538
Unfortunately, there are some believers
who think they know Jesus and the faith

00:25:51.538 --> 00:25:54.660
better than bishops, better than the Pope.

00:25:54.660 --> 00:25:56.890
I've encountered such people myself.

00:25:56.890 --> 00:25:59.120
They interpret, they know everything.

00:25:59.120 --> 00:26:04.027
They consider themselves to be more
Catholic than the Pope himself.

00:26:04.027 --> 00:26:10.718
For example, there's a good example, I
don't know how much you've heard about it.

00:26:10.718 --> 00:26:16.516
There are people within the Church
who spread the "Book of Truth" and

00:26:16.516 --> 00:26:20.085
talk about the seal of the living God.

00:26:21.524 --> 00:26:23.414
What is the problem here?

00:26:23.414 --> 00:26:28.703
The Church has warned countless times
that this "book of truth" is not a

00:26:28.703 --> 00:26:34.748
book of truth and that there is only
one seal, not the seal of the living

00:26:34.748 --> 00:26:40.416
God as they interpret it, but the seal
of the sacrament, the seal of baptism.

00:26:40.416 --> 00:26:43.061
And beyond that, nothing more is needed.

00:26:43.061 --> 00:26:47.595
Yet they remain stubborn and disobedient
to the Church, disobedient to Christ.

00:26:47.595 --> 00:26:52.129
And how many such people do we
have within the Catholic Church

00:26:52.129 --> 00:26:57.040
who listen to someone else, not the
Church hierarchy, not the Holy Spirit

00:26:57.040 --> 00:26:58.930
who speaks through the hierarchy?

00:26:59.430 --> 00:27:05.308
But they will say, I know better than
the bishop, I know better than the

00:27:05.308 --> 00:27:08.052
Pope, I know better than this priest.

00:27:08.052 --> 00:27:11.971
You see how often that
phrase "I know" is used.

00:27:11.971 --> 00:27:17.458
I've often encountered people who, when
they want to boast about their faith, say,

00:27:17.458 --> 00:27:22.945
I know this bishop, I was good friends
with that priest, I'm great, top-notch.

00:27:23.125 --> 00:27:26.221
But you see, that's
superficial, just knowing.

00:27:26.221 --> 00:27:28.876
Don't let that word deceive you.

00:27:28.876 --> 00:27:35.512
Don't let that word deceive you, because
what I said about this book, the book

00:27:35.512 --> 00:27:39.493
of truth and the seal of the living God.

00:27:39.493 --> 00:27:42.590
People, why did I focus on this?

00:27:42.590 --> 00:27:47.899
Because it's spreading more and
more in Croatia, and the church is

00:27:47.899 --> 00:27:54.093
warning, but some are deaf, they don't
want to hear the truth, they live

00:27:54.093 --> 00:27:57.190
in lies and drag others into lies.

00:27:57.670 --> 00:28:00.218
And why is that not good?

00:28:00.218 --> 00:28:06.589
The author of that book claims that God
directly told her the words to write.

00:28:06.589 --> 00:28:11.686
But the Second Vatican Council states
that the Bible wasn't directly dictated

00:28:11.686 --> 00:28:16.783
by Jesus; rather, it says that divinely
inspired people wrote the scriptures.

00:28:16.783 --> 00:28:22.729
And when you compare, you realise that
her book seems more authoritative than the

00:28:22.729 --> 00:28:28.675
Bible, because in her case everything is
direct and nothing can be changed, whereas

00:28:28.675 --> 00:28:34.622
here there is room to discern what the
Holy Spirit inspired and what individual

00:28:34.622 --> 00:28:37.170
authors wrote in their own words.

00:28:37.170 --> 00:28:38.445
Do you understand?

00:28:39.005 --> 00:28:44.008
And how difficult it is today, we
must speak the truth but some will

00:28:44.008 --> 00:28:46.152
want to listen and some won't.

00:28:46.152 --> 00:28:49.369
And here we also see the Kingdom of God.

00:28:49.369 --> 00:28:55.445
If I talk about the Kingdom of God, then
I am subject to Jesus Christ, to His

00:28:55.445 --> 00:28:58.304
word, and I only believe in the Gospel.

00:28:58.304 --> 00:29:03.665
And as Saint Paul says, let me be
cursed if I preach a different gospel.

00:29:04.115 --> 00:29:10.372
So, brothers and sisters, we must be
cautious and vigilant so that the spirit

00:29:10.372 --> 00:29:13.948
of this world does not lead us astray.

00:29:13.948 --> 00:29:14.395
Amen.

